{"TopicId":187318,"ForumId":109,"TopicTitle":"Hopes and Wishes for KSP 2","CreatedByName":"Elthy","CreatedById":63317,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T18:39:39Z","PageNum":32,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-09T23:34:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMultiple launch sites (at multiple latitudes), with reasons to use them:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nCertain manufacturer\u0027s parts are cheaper (or more expensive) at certain sites to account for travel costs, making some sites more lucrative.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nContracts stating to launch from a specific site because \u003Cs\u003Ethe congressman is from that district\u003C/s\u003E the relevant infrastructure for the ground base is there.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nContracts to launch and pilot payloads from 2 different sites in order to dock them.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\netc?\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lewie","CreatedById":203745,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-10T01:09:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll I want from Ksp2 alongside rocket engines if ridiculous proportions, is the original guys. Good \u2018ol Jeb, Bill and Bob. I want to strap Jeb onto like an orion drive rocket and have him hurtle gleefully through the cosmos...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ac1ionm4n","CreatedById":203917,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-10T18:23:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy only hope is that it comes out soon...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qwerbo","CreatedById":200269,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-11T14:33:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want a colony building facility on the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E and cities with city lights on Kerbin and habitable exoplanets.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qwerbo","CreatedById":200269,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-11T14:43:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen will KSP2 come? The page only say 2020.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-04-11T14:44:37Z\u0022 title=\u002204/11/2020 02:44  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EApril 11, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by qwerbo\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lewie","CreatedById":203745,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-11T18:00:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223769461\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187318\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221586615636\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022200269\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022qwerbo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, qwerbo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want a colony building facility on the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E and cities with city lights on Kerbin and habitable exoplanets.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShadow zone posted an interview he did with Nate Simpson\u00A0and he described that colony building\u00A0would be like the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E but it would be on the planet/moon. Does that help at all?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-04-11T18:04:15Z\u0022 title=\u002204/11/2020 06:04  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EApril 11, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Lewie\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EI didn\u2019t remember the name of the star theroy director. Oops\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Seffy","CreatedById":203939,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-12T00:00:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope the\u00A0aviation psychics will better. I know that\u0027s not the main game but it\u0027s like Simpleplanes and Simplerockits together.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lewie","CreatedById":203745,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-12T00:01:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223769705\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187318\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221586649627\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022203939\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Seffy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Seffy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope the\u00A0aviation psychics will better. I know that\u0027s not the main game but it\u0027s like Simpleplanes and Simplerockits together.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntoo true brother. too true.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tsamsiyu","CreatedById":204158,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-22T07:43:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would love to se a 3d printing mechanic, where you can mine stuff from asteroids, planets and\u00A0moons refine them and then you can use them to 3d print your parts there. could be fun to build a self suffitient colony with this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-04-22T07:47:23Z\u0022 title=\u002204/22/2020 07:47  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EApril 22, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Tsamsiyu\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mamboo07","CreatedById":204166,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-23T08:51:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope that we might get Saturn, Uranus and Neptune as well Pluto and the 5 other dwarf planets including Sedna and also the hypothetical Planet Nine\u00A0for the Kerbol System.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"evilducky","CreatedById":82523,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-23T15:37:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLong time lurker here: IDK if this has been mentioned but I recently got into the mod \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Attachment System (mod)\u0022\u003EKAS\u003C/abbr\u003E and \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Inventory System (mod)\u0022\u003EKIS\u003C/abbr\u003E. These 2 mods have changed KSP for me to a point where I don\u0027t think I could go back to stock. I really hope this idea carries over to KSP2\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Incarnation of Chaos","CreatedById":197414,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-23T17:50:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223769705\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187318\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221586649627\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022203939\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Seffy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/11/2020 at 7:00 PM, Seffy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope the\u00A0aviation psychics will better. I know that\u0027s not the main game but it\u0027s like Simpleplanes and Simplerockits together.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey\u0027re using the same broken, massively simplified aero model that KSP1 has, and that\u0027s been confirmed for a long time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Seffy","CreatedById":203939,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-24T19:51:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223774949\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187318\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221587664204\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197414\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Incarnation of Chaos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/23/2020 at 1:50 PM, Incarnation of Chaos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey\u0027re using the same broken, massively simplified aero model that KSP1 has, and that\u0027s been confirmed for a long time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh. Well I guess\u00A0my dreams of making a plane that can actually stay wings level are broken.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lewie","CreatedById":203745,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-24T19:53:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAwww man. I would love to have Jeb, Val, Bill and Bob back. Otherwise...what\u2019s Ksp without Jeb?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Seffy","CreatedById":203939,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-24T19:55:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223774756\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187318\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221587631890\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204166\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mamboo07\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/23/2020 at 4:51 AM, Mamboo07 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope that we might get Saturn, Uranus and Neptune as well Pluto and the 5 other dwarf planets including Sedna and also the hypothetical Planet Nine\u00A0for the Kerbol System.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike they make planets\u00A0that are\u00A0similar or make an actual replica?\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223775507\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187318\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221587757983\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022203745\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lewie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Lewie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAwww man. I would love to have Jeb, Val, Bill and Bob back. Otherwise...what\u2019s Ksp without Jeb?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWait, what!? No Jeb, Val, Bill or \u00A0Bob!? What\u2019s even the point any more?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lewie","CreatedById":203745,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-24T19:59:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223775511\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187318\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221587758104\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022203939\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Seffy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Seffy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWait, what!? No Jeb, Val, Bill or \u00A0Bob!? What\u2019s even the point any more?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf Star Theory doesn\u2019t include there won\u2019t be a point, my dude.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Seffy","CreatedById":203939,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-24T20:19:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/203745-lewie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022203745\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/203745-lewie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Lewie\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0I thought Val was in the\u00A0trailer. Isn\u2019t she the one that\u2019s on Mun? IGN says that Val.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-04-24T20:21:03Z\u0022 title=\u002204/24/2020 08:21  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EApril 24, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Seffy\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lewie","CreatedById":203745,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-24T20:42:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have no idea my dude. I can\u2019t tell the difference between Kerbals. So...no idea.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dirkidirk","CreatedById":200064,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-24T21:01:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223775522\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187318\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221587759582\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022203939\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Seffy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n42 minutes ago, Seffy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/203745-lewie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022203745\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/203745-lewie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Lewie\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0I thought Val was in the\u00A0trailer. Isn\u2019t she the one that\u2019s on Mun? IGN says that Val.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nit doesn\u0027t really look like vall tho, the haircut looks\u00A0different to me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-04-24T21:02:04Z\u0022 title=\u002204/24/2020 09:02  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EApril 24, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Dirkidirk\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Seffy","CreatedById":203939,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-24T21:14:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223775540\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187318\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221587762105\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022200064\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dirkidirk\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, Dirkidirk said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nit doesn\u0027t really look like vall tho, the haircut looks\u00A0different to me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u2019t know. IGN said that was Val and they also said you could customize your kerbals\u00A0haircuts or something like that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lewie","CreatedById":203745,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-24T22:47:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nId you can customize kerbal hair cuts....heck, Imma gonna use cheats to create kerbals named John, Paul, George, and Ringo. And I\u2019ll give \u2018em beatles style haircuts. And send them hurtling through the cosmos. THE BEATLES WILL BE REUNITED AND STUCK TOGETHER FOR PROBABLY A COUPLE HUNDRED YEARS!!! \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Seffy","CreatedById":203939,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-25T00:55:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223775569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187318\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221587768430\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022203745\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lewie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Lewie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nId you can customize kerbal hair cuts....heck, Imma gonna use cheats to create kerbals named John, Paul, George, and Ringo. And I\u2019ll give \u2018em beatles style haircuts. And send them hurtling through the cosmos. THE BEATLES WILL BE REUNITED AND STUCK TOGETHER FOR PROBABLY A COUPLE HUNDRED YEARS!!! \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaha,\u00A0nice.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lewie","CreatedById":203745,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-25T20:03:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would also like too add that I hope all of the intresting sites from ksp (Neil Armstrong memoiral, Vall henge, etc.) will be implemented into ksp2 with hopefully more sites to find. Also, I hope that the devs don\u0027t mess with the gravity of kerbin or any of the planets, or change up any of the atmospheres.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sebegg","CreatedById":204291,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-28T02:17:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMore Flags\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll I want is at least a SpaceX flag that i can use\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nand if it isn\u0027t too much trouble can we have a custom flag making system\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sebegg","CreatedById":204291,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-28T02:20:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223768663\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187318\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221586475253\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Superfluous J\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/10/2020 at 9:34 AM, Superfluous J said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMultiple launch sites (at multiple latitudes), with reasons to use them:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nCertain manufacturer\u0027s parts are cheaper (or more expensive) at certain sites to account for travel costs, making some sites more lucrative.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nContracts stating to launch from a specific site because \u003Cs\u003Ethe congressman is from that district\u003C/s\u003E the relevant infrastructure for the ground base is there.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nContracts to launch and pilot payloads from 2 different sites in order to dock them.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\netc?\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think it would be cool if you had to buy these extra launch sites in career mode since having multiple right away would make it too easy to dock ships and make interplantery missions\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}